title: [Boreas Hills, Mistral Court]
description: The street ends here where several homes are snuggled into the mountainside.  More homes rest on either side of this small square, while a small marble fountain sits in the middle, water cheerfully cascading down the tiers to pool at the bottom.

The street ends here where several homes are snuggled into the mountainside.  More homes rest on either side of this small square, their windows bright with light. A small marble fountain sits in the middle of the square, the water silvery in the moonlight.
